  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para:~]
[begin:note]
[:en] The [`text_encoding::id] enumeration contains an enumerator for each known
registered character encoding.
[:zh_CN] [`text_encoding::id] 枚举包含每个已知注册字符编码的枚举符。

[:en] For each encoding, the corresponding enumerator is derived from
the alias beginning with [=lq][`cs][=rq], as follows:
[:zh_CN] 对于每种编码，其对应枚举符是从以“[`cs]”开头的别名导出的，方法如下：
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] [`csUnicode] is mapped to [`text_encoding::id::UCS2],
[:zh_CN@~] [`csUnicode] 映射为 [`text_encoding::id::UCS2]。
[item]
[:en@~] [`csIBBM904] is mapped to [`text_encoding::id::IBM904], and
[:zh_CN@~] [`csIBBM904] 映射为 [`text_encoding::id::IBM904]，而
[item]
[:en@~] the [=lq][`cs][=rq] prefix is removed from other names.
[:zh_CN@~] 从其他名字中移除“[`cs]”前缀。
[list:end]
[end:note]
